OL,3,CFour teenagers charged with arson
OL,4,Cattack at college
OL,6,FFour teenagers have been charged in
OL,7,Fconnection with a fire at Henley
OL,8,FCollege.
OL,10,FExtensive damage was caused to the
OL,11,Fformer Coventry College campus during
OL,12,Fthe blaze on 29 April last year, which
OL,13,Ftore through the site.
OL,15,FPolice have confirmed that four
OL,16,Fteenagers have been charged with arson.
OL,18,FThe two boys and two girls are 15 and
OL,19,F16 respectively and cannot be named
OL,20,Ffor legal reasons.
