OL,3,CFour teenagers charged with arson
OL,4,Cattack at college
OL,6,FAll four are due to appear before
OL,7,Fmagistrates in Coventry on 4 June.
OL,9,FA spokesperson from West Midlands
OL,10,FPolice said: "Four teenagers have been
OL,11,Fcharged in connection with a serious
OL,12,Ffire at a former college in Coventry.
OL,14,F"The fire at the former college site
OL,15,Fin Henley Road, happened on 29 April
OL,16,Flast year and caused extensive damage
OL,17,Fto the site.
OL,19,F"Now two boys and two girls aged 15
OL,20,Fand 16 respectively, have been charged
OL,21,Fwith arson.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
